    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute perfection. It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, runs like a dream, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a reliable, great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner very happy! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
