    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis remains composed thanks to proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring optimal thermal management during spirited driving. This is a mechanically sound example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
